message: "A 31-year-old Lake Worth man was arrested last week after DNA evidence linked him to a case involving a teenage human-trafficking victim, according to a Palm Beach County Sheriff’s Office arrest report."

data.description: The charge stemmed from a 2017 investigation involving a girl, then 15 years old, the Palm Beach County Sheriff's Office said.
data.title: Lake Worth man accused of lewd behavior on human-trafficking victim
